<section class="xl-section xl-faq-section">
    <div class="xl-container xl-faq-container">
        <div class="xl-section-header">
            <div class="xl-eyebrow">FAQ</div>
            <h2>Pricing questions.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="xl-faq-grid">
            <details class="xl-faq-item">
                <summary>Do I need an account to use ExcelToolStack?</summary>
                <p>Free tools work without any account. AI tools, batch processing, and download history require a Pro account. Signing up takes under a minute via Google, GitHub, or email.</p>
            </details>
            <details class="xl-faq-item">
                <summary>What's included in the Bundle plan?</summary>
                <p>The Bundle gives you Pro access to both ExcelToolStack and PdfToolStack under one subscription. That means AI Formula Copilot, AI workbook review, AI invoice extraction, AI contract review, and batch processing across both products.</p>
            </details>
            <details class="xl-faq-item">
                <summary>Can I cancel anytime?</summary>
                <p>Yes — cancel anytime from your account page. Your access continues until the end of the billing period. No cancellation fees.</p>
            </details>
            <details class="xl-faq-item">
                <summary>Is there an annual discount?</summary>
                <p>Yes — annual plans are approximately 33% less than monthly. The annual pricing is shown at checkout.</p>
            </details>
            <details class="xl-faq-item">
                <summary>How does the Teams plan work?</summary>
                <p>Teams includes 5 seats, a shared workspace, and an admin dashboard for usage tracking. Additional seats are $6/month each. Billing is at the account level, not per user.</p>
            </details>
            <details class="xl-faq-item">
                <summary>Is my data safe?</summary>
                <p>Uploaded files are processed securely and never stored permanently. We don't train AI models on your data and don't share files with third parties.</p>
            </details>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="xl-footer-cta">
    <div class="xl-container">
        <h2>Start free — no credit card required.</h2>
        <p>Core tools work immediately. Upgrade to Pro when you need AI and batch processing.</p>
        <a href="/tools" class="xl-btn-primary xl-btn-large">Start for free →</a>
    </div>
</section>
